          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": "وَقَالَ اَلصَّادِقُ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ: «إِنَّ أَعْدَاءَنَا يَمُوتُونَ بِالطَّاعُونِ"
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": " وَ "
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": "أَنْتُمْ تَمُوتُونَ بِعِلَّةِ اَلْبُطُونِ أَلاَ إِنَّهَا عَلاَمَةٌ"
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": " فِي"
          }
        ]
      },
      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/man-la-yahduruhu-al-faqih:1:28:21",
      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/1/28/578",
      "text": [
        "كُمْ يَا مَعْشَرَ اَلشِّيعَةِ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.578 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) said:\n\"Our enemies die of plague, while you (our Shi’ite) die of ailments of the stomach. Verily, this is a sign among you, O’ group of Shi'a.\""
        ]
      }
